               <msContents>
                  <summary>I) Dǝrsāna Mikāʾel, Homiliary for the feasts of St Michael (fols.
                     3r-95v)
 I–1) Homily by Timothy (Damātewos) of Alexandria for the 12th day
                     of Ḫǝdār (fols. 3ra-9ra l.3); two miracles (fols. 9ra l.4-10rb l.1);
                     commemorative notice (fols. 10rb l.2-11vb l.18) 
 I–2) Anonymous homily for
                     the 12th day of Tāḫśāś (fols. 11vb l.19-16vb); miracle (fol. 17ra-vb l.5);
                     commemorative notice (fols. 17vb l.6-18va l.3) 
 I–3) Anonymous homily for
                     the 12th day of Ṭǝrr (fols. 18va l.4-27ra l.5); miracle (fols. 27ra l.6-28vb
                     l.17); commemorative notice (fols. 27vb l.18-28ra l.11) 
 I–4) Anonymous
                     homily for the 12th day of Yakkātit (fols. 28ra l.12-31ra l.13); miracle (fols.
                     31ra l.14-32ra l.2); commemorative notice (fol. 32ra l.3-vb l.2) 
 I–5)
                     Homily by Patriarch John of Antiochia for the 12th day of Maggābit (fols. 32vb
                     l.3-46rb l.17); miracle (fols. 46rb l.18-49vb l.2); commemorative notice (fols.
                     49vb l.3-50ra l.8) 
 I–6) [Homily by John the Orthodox for the 12th of
                     Miyāzyā] (fols. 50ra l.9-54rb), miracle (fols. 54va-56vb l.5); commemorative
                     notice (fols. 56vb l.6-57rb l.5) 
 I–7) Homily by Yoḥannǝs, Metropolitan of
                     Ethiopia for the 12th of Gǝnbot (fols. 57rb l.6-59ra l.5); miracle (fols. 59ra
                     l.6-61ra l.12); commemorative notice (fol. 61ra l.13-vb l.10) 
 I–8) Homily
                     by Yoḥannǝs, Metropolitan of Aksum for the 12th day of Sane (fols. 61vb
                     l.11-74va l.11); miracle (fol. 74va l.4-vb l.2); commemorative notice (fols.
                     74vb l.3-76ra l.2) 
 I–9) Homily of Bishop John for the 12th day of Ḥamle
                     (fols. 76ra l.3-80ra l.3); miracle (fol. 80ra l.3-vb l.8); commemorative notice
                     (fols. 80vb l.9-81rb l.15) 
 I–10) Homily by an anonymous author for the
                     12th day of Naḥāse (fols. 81rb l.16-84ra l.13); miracle (fol. 84ra l.14-vb
                     l.12); commemorative notice (fols. 84vb l.13-85ra l.1) 
 I–11) Anonymous
                     homily for the 12th day of Maskaram (fols. 85ra l.1-87va l.14); miracle (fols.
                     87va l.15-89va l.14); commemorative notice (fol. 89va l.15-vb) 
 I–12)
                     Anonymous homily for the 12th day of Ṭǝqǝmt (fols. 90ra-93rb l.5); miracle
                     (fols. 93rb l.6-94vb l.9); commemorative notice (fols. 94vb l.10-95vb)
                     
 Additio 1.</summary>
