               <provenance>The donor, Walda Māryām, is mentioned in
                     Additio 1 and in the supplication formulas. His father, Gabra Wahǝd, and his
                     mother, Walatta ʾAnanya, are also mentioned. Other names appear in the
                     supplication formulas, such as Fǝśśǝḥa Giyorgis (e.g., 17ra, 31ra), Gabra ʾIyasus (28ra),
                     Walatta Śǝllāse (28ra, 59ra).</provenance></history>
